Title: Anasazi (1)
Plot: When Mulder obtains what could be the original and uncut MJ documents containing information about the government's knowledge of extraterrestrial life; his shadowy enemies step up their harassment of him, eventually leading to his apparent murder.
GuestStars: Chris Carter, Bernie Coulson, Aurelio Dinunzio, Paul McLean, Byron Chief-Moon, Renae Morriseau, Ken Camroux, Mitchell Davies, Dakota House
